  <summary date="2025-02-05T15:28:21Z" status="Introduced in House">Injunctive Authority Clarification Act of 2025&#160;

This bill prohibits federal courts from issuing injunctive orders that bar enforcement of a federal law or policy against a nonparty, unless the nonparty is represented by a party in a class action lawsuit.</summary>
